Room tour 

Hi darling, this is my temporary apartment.

It's a fancy room, and very specious for me.

First, let take a look the bathroom.

It's not only a restroom, here is a shower, I take shower here every day.

this is a mirror, I could look at myself with it. seems I need to clean up my beard.

this is toilet, because I eat fresh vegetables every day, so I use it every day as well.

Okay, then we go to the bedroom. this is my bed, it has a lamp

there's a dresser, I put my clothes and luggages on it.

Well, the next one is kitchen.

this is the oven, I used it many times a day. heat the milk, and pizza, and fried chicken and so on.

below the oven, this is a refrigerator. I stored some milk and cheese in it.

